{"tid":1790442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙里爆粗大讚C朗入樽式頭槌：黐X線","createTime":"2019-12-20T03:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T04:42:38.000Z","uid":34293,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ecd926bb2bee7d5fd7e377fc813732ab9ad01e3","tid":1790442,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTFGUc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTFGUc8.jpg&h=f42f12d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度在昨日對森多利亞一戰攻入一記精彩的頭槌，這一個盡展其空中霸王本色的入球亦叫不少人拍案叫盡。祖雲達斯主帥沙里甚至在記日會上以「黐X線」形容這一個入球。<br />\n<br />\n對於C朗以跳起離地2.56米之多頂入，沙里不得不「爆粗」形容這一球：「當C朗入這一球時，我心中跟戴巴拿入球時所想一樣，就是『嘩，黐X線』。單時嘩已經不能形容這入球有多精彩了。戴巴拿以左腳窩利的方式處理了一個99％人會先控定的攻勢。而C朗那一球的騰空時間非常長，是一個結合體力與技術的入球。」"},{"pid":"7b5d90fd4ec1609cddda8124a37761fcb6c15a43","tid":1790442,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe8555881232a45c6383ab4974fdf3784d2f980","tid":1790442,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"學左王騎?"},{"pid":"fb7c522c082b4cb0ed3cbfa6125c54bc5bbe6a67","tid":1790442,"uid":336453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"沙利中文咁好既咩"},{"pid":"410235cc1b9bb0ddd2f55db42fc135d669592375","tid":1790442,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"美斯大讚華維迪調動：屌你老X"},{"pid":"b907b3590d879448be6df42e561275bf1f647a2c","tid":1790442,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"有冇原文學吓嘢"},{"pid":"bc642d784faa60cc1f37af2341505724453ae263","tid":1790442,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410235cc1b9bb0ddd2f55db42fc135d669592375","tid":1790442,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"美斯大讚華維迪調動：屌你老X"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6634c16cb321bdd97762523fc7c24b12a65d99","tid":1790442,"uid":77580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410235cc1b9bb0ddd2f55db42fc135d669592375","tid":1790442,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"美斯大讚華維迪調動：屌你老X"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98f50b4447fa8b3534ea063bb51cbb1e90b72a2","tid":1790442,"uid":68689,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥在10月4日對香港制定一記精彩的蒙面法條例，這一個盡展其政治本色的立法亦叫不少人拍案叫盡。香港特別行政區政務司司長張建宗甚至在記者會上以「黐X線」形容這一個條例。<br />\n<br />\n對於林鄭月娥以一日之多立法，張建宗不得不「爆粗」形容這一球：「當林鄭立法時，我心中跟制定引渡條例時所想一樣，就是『嘩，黐X線』。單時嘩已經不能形容對香港人有多精彩了。引渡條例以強硬的方式處理了一個200萬香港人會反對的攻勢。而林鄭蒙面法的制定時間非常短，是一個結合焦土與攬炒的立法。」"},{"pid":"68995604f8553493bb7aa7f3ca49502731297576","tid":1790442,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e6634c16cb321bdd97762523fc7c24b12a65d99","tid":1790442,"uid":77580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410235cc1b9bb0ddd2f55db42fc135d669592375","tid":1790442,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"美斯大讚華維迪調動：屌你老X"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"原片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.beinsports.com/us/serie-a/video/sarri-stunned-by-ronaldos-headed-goal/1372784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.be